data.description: Come see this charming cottage that is FHA financeable at an incredible value. Nestled between Rogue Community College and Downtown Grants Pass. This home features a large 1,300 sq/ft living space with 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and attic space for storage or potentially a 3rd bedroom. Tons of ADA features like a gentle ramp on the side for easy no step living that is convenient for everyone. Recently updated with new vinyl flooring in the bathroom, kitchen, laundry room, and water heater closet. New flooring in the living room. New ADA friendly shower with built in teakwood seat with dual shower heads. Brand new triple vinyl windows. Brand new gas furnace and hot water heater recently as well. New partial fencing in the backyard.
